Tutorial Mod Development Notes

========================================================================================================================
-------------------------------------------          CREATIVE TABS          -------------------------------------------
========================================================================================================================

ModCreativeModeTabs
    * Create a new tab by copying an existing registration (Line 16-27).
    * Line 16 - Change the registry name.
    * Line 17 - Change the tab identifier.
    * Line 18 - Change the icon item.
    * Line 19 - Change the displayed tab name.
        * Add the translation key to en_us.json.
    * Line 21-24 - Add or remove items from the Creative Tab.


========================================================================================================================
-----------------------------------------------          Items          -----------------------------------------------
========================================================================================================================

1. ModModelProvider
    * Line 22 - Copy an existing generatedItem() entry.
    * Rename it to the new item ID.
    * Generates the item model during DataGen.

2. ModItems
    * Line 18 - Register the new item.
    * Set any item properties (durability, stack size, rarity, food, etc.).

3. ModCreativeModeTabs
    * Line 32
        * Select which Creative Tab the item belongs to.
    * Line 35
        * Add the item to the selected Creative Tab.

4. en_us.json
    * Line 2 - Add the in-game display name.

5. Textures
    * Add the item texture (.png).

6. Data Generation
    * Run DataGen.


========================================================================================================================
--------------------------------------------          Custom Items          --------------------------------------------
========================================================================================================================

1. Create a new Java class inside:
    item/custom

    Useful Tips
        * Type "override" to view available item interactions.
        * Press CTRL + H on Item to view the Minecraft item class hierarchy.

2. ModItems
    * Line 21 - Register the custom item.
    * Add custom properties such as durability.

3. ModCreativeModeTabs
    * Line 24 - Add the item to the Creative Tab.

4. ModModelProvider
    * Line 34 - Register the handheld item model.

5. Add
    * Texture
    * en_us.json translation

6. Run DataGen


========================================================================================================================
--------------------------------------------          Custom Food          --------------------------------------------
========================================================================================================================

1. Create a new Java class inside:
    item/custom

    Useful Tips
        * Double Shift
        * Enable "Include Non-Project Items"
        * Search:
            - FoodProperties
            - Consumable

    These classes control:
        * Nutrition
        * Saturation
        * Eat/Drink animation
        * Eat duration
        * Sounds
        * Status effects
        * Effect chance

2. Register in

    ModFoods
        * FoodProperties
        * Consumable

    ModItems
        * Register the item.

    ModCreativeModeTabs
        * Add to Creative Tab.

    ModModelProvider
        * Generate model.

    Add
        * Texture
        * en_us.json

3. Run DataGen


