========================================================================================================================
------------------------------------------          DATA COMPONENTS          ------------------------------------------
========================================================================================================================

ModDataComponents
    * Register custom Data Components.

Example

    COORDINATES
        * Stores List<BlockPos>.
        * Used by the Chisel to remember selected blocks.

TutorialMod
    * Register ModDataComponents during mod initialization.

Example Usage (ChiselItem)

    * Store selected blocks.
    * Remove selected blocks.
    * Read stored blocks.
    * Display custom tooltips.

ModModelProvider
    * Can swap item models based on Data Component values.


