========================================================================================================================
--------------------------------------------          CUSTOM TAGS          --------------------------------------------
========================================================================================================================

Tags are reusable lists of Items or Blocks.

Benefits

    * Cleaner code.
    * Easier maintenance.
    * Better compatibility with other mods.

Example

    MagicBlock
        * Line 65
        * Uses a Tag instead of a hardcoded block list.